auss','[core] check if client half-closed tcp if pollhup (#2743)  check if client half-closed tcp connection if pollhup is received. this more robustly handles if client called shutdown(fd, shut_wr).  this patch reverts commit:ab05eb7c which should now be handled properly. (time will tell.)  x-ref:   \"1.4.40/41 mod_proxy, mod_scgi may trigger pollhup on *bsd,darwin\"   https://redmine.lighttpd.net/issues/2743','connections.c','969','253','21','37','false','false','false','2016-08-06 04:28:45-04:00'),('lighttpd','1.4.40','4bc06bfc0b72b92c67f21ac0dc7de7d67be73728','Glenn Strauss','[core] check if client half-closed tcp if pollhup (#2743)  check if client half-closed tcp connection if pollhup is received. this more robustly handles if client called shutdown(fd, shut_wr).  this patch reverts commit:ab05eb7c which should now be handled properly. (time will tell.)  x-ref:   \"1.4.40/41 mod_proxy, mod_scgi may trigger pollhup on *bsd,darwin\"   https://redmine.lighttpd.net/issues/2743','fdevent.c','207','73','32','0','false','true','false','2016-08-06 04:28:45-04:00'),('lighttpd','1.4.40','4bc06bfc0b72b92c67f21ac0dc7de7d67be73728','Glenn Strauss','[core] check if client half-closed tcp if pollhup (#2743)  check if client half-closed tcp connection if pollhup is received. this more robustly handles if client called shutdown(fd, shut_wr).  this patch reverts commit:ab05eb7c which should now be handled properly. (time will tell.)  x-ref:   \"1.4.40/41 mod_proxy, mod_scgi may trigger pollhup on *bsd,darwin\"   https://redmine.lighttpd.net/issues/2743','fdevent.h','102','0','3','0','false','false','false','2016-08-06 04:28:45-04:00'),('lighttpd','1.4.40','4bc06bfc0b72b92c67f21ac0dc7de7d67be73728','Glenn Strauss','[core] check if client half-closed tcp if pollhup (#2743)  check if client half-closed tcp connection if pollhup is received. this more robustly handles if client called shutdown(fd, shut_wr).  this patch reverts commit:ab05eb7c which should now be handled properly. (